text.en_US:
left click
a potion
to pick it up

then left click on
another shelf
to place it there

Click on the bell to
start the day!

hello,
nice little shop
you have!

may I have a 
health potion?

rise and shine
it's a new day

children.memo:
the chosen potion to give to the NPC
default 0 = nothing
1 = health potion
2 = poison potion
children.name: chosenPotion

children.memo: how much money the player has
children.name: money

children.memo: how many people that are poisoned "it's spreading"
children.name: peoplePoisoned

children.memo:
default: 360

the time left untill night counted seconds
children.name: timeLeftTilNight
startDay
children.memo: boolean to check if the day is started

children.name: counterActive
children.memo: checks if there's an NPC in front of the counter

children.name: serve
children.memo:
when this is true, the dialogue box will take the current item in the counter object
and then it will make a dialogue according to the item

children.name: startCrafting
children.memo: this switch will start the crafting process

children.name: dialogue finished
children.memo: checks if the dialogue is finished for today
